{"tid":113343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只有香港人會為左\"食邊篤屎\"而爭論不休","createTime":"2017-02-09T01:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T08:49:10.000Z","uid":57376,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01f7e69f5669a7295deb0cb3e040bf7a034212ff","tid":113343,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:33:27.000Z","msg":"明明都係要食屎，但有d人好奇怪，鍾意理人地想食邊篤屎，有d仲要係度分析篤屎表面同入面有咩分別，順便笑人唔識食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似唔記得自己都食緊屎咁，然後最神奇係仲會有人為篤屎打氣，甚至捐錢俾人整篤屎自己食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本正常黎講，反對食屎or含淚食屎先係人類應有表現，但香港人已經進化到可以投入食屎哩個過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42642956eed114f0e18138cc2e6e3d47b0a489c","tid":113343,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a343ebc67e7b1a379a00734fa7595a98f42584","tid":113343,"uid":33989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ab72405dc991a132c24fbae203ef5563252c7d","tid":113343,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:50:53.000Z","msg":"班人係咪扮睇唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750af112520ceb61d92f3de5d7e62844a91cbb26","tid":113343,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"我之前都話過香港人食屎可以好滋味滿足"},{"pid":"4acd9cbde88b5d968eae2e3ac1c55c86a8b27683","tid":113343,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前都話過香港人食屎可以好滋味滿足</blockquote><br />\n就算你有心換牛屎整鬼佢地<br />\n佢地一樣食到好滿足，用表情直接黎撚化返你"},{"pid":"a81cfa8413e444196485bd0396b1dc2246e738be","tid":113343,"uid":71058,"lik