ts/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本正常黎講，反對食屎or含淚食屎先係人類應有表現，但香港人已經進化到可以投入食屎哩個過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後係冇人會理班人揀邊舊屎 夾硬塞舊屎你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cc2642eb9a76d76b850904a9c83d24baa263b5","tid":113343,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"食屎都要加錢要shakeshake粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378782aa93567ecf436d79ccf0980305c6c7fe4f","tid":113343,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"最好笑係有人可以懶清高扮到唔關佢事，但又明明住喺同一個屎坑食緊屎"},{"pid":"f74a2d5bd5a92228c5e0b1ba24ccff0c59469a7a","tid":113343,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比喻不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢舊屎係一定要食</blockquote><br />\n我有話可以唔食咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c831827c4d4ef820599a21d1480654830479b5","tid":113343,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好笑係有人可以懶清高扮到唔關佢事，但又明明住喺同一個屎坑食緊屎</blockquote><br />\n希望你唔係話緊我，因為我上面已經有講正常人類一係就反抗食屎，一係就含淚食屎，前者靠我一個無用，所以我選擇後者，但至少唔會扮清高咁評論人地食邊篤屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09892a628fc4a0ff8f4c882dbef65fe60f954fa7","tid":113343,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"所以我從來無係食屎post度留過言"},{"pid":"858bc2f3568dfb8ec2bb2aad0c861043462d5f70","tid":113343,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"你今日含左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e1fe88e567b969971b9012a6d5ea91a01999a0","tid":1